[summary unrecommended_profile]
Current tuning profile is &tune_profile;. Recommended profile is 'enterprise-storage'

[explanation unrecommended_profile]
Current tuning profile is &tune_profile;. Recommended profile is 'enterprise-storage'.
	'enterprise-storage' is a server profile to improve throughput performance for enterprise-sized server configurations. This switches to the deadline IO scheduler and disables certain I/O barriers, dramatically improving throughput. 

[solution unrecommended_profile]
As root user, change the tuning profile to 'enterprise-storage' by running
	# tuned-adm profile enterprise-storage

[reference unrecommended_profile]
See the tuned-adm man page for futher details on available profiles.
